 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/ruud-sabalenka-light-up-roland-garros-after-rain-wreaks-havoc-schedule-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>爱沙尼亚称中国尚未回应海底电缆调查请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/estonia-says-china-has-not-responded-subsea-cables-probe-request-2024-05-28/</link><description>爱沙尼亚国家检察官表示，中国尚未回应六个月前就调查一艘中国船只的请求，爱沙尼亚怀疑这艘船切断了其两条海底电信电缆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:42:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/estonia-says-china-has-not-responded-subsea-cables-probe-request-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车将开发低成本电动汽车应对中国竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-develop-entry-level-electric-vehicles-around-20000-euros-2024-05-28/</link><description>欧洲最大的汽车制造商在本月初与雷诺合作该项目的谈判破裂后，周二表示，大众汽车将开发低成本电动汽车，以更好地与激烈的中国竞争对手竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-develop-entry-level-electric-vehicles-around-20000-euros-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京拒绝美国对中国生产过剩的评估</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russias-putin-rejects-us-assessment-chinas-overproduction-2024-05-28/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京驳斥了美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦对中国产能过剩和汽车生产过剩对全球经济影响的担忧，认为这种担忧是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russias-putin-rejects-us-assessment-chinas-overproduction-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：阿根廷有望于七月开始向中国出口玉米——谷物商会负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/argentina-track-start-corn-exports-china-july-grains-chamber-head-2024-05-28/</link><description>阿根廷粮食出口商会周二告诉路透社，阿根廷有望从 7 月份开始向中国出口期待已久的玉米，这对这个世界第一大南美国家来说将是一个重大推动。 3 粮食供应商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/argentina-track-start-corn-exports-china-july-grains-chamber-head-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国法院将于 9 月听取对 TikTok 潜在禁令的质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-hear-challenges-potential-tiktok-ban-september-2024-05-28/</link><description>美国上诉法院周二制定了一个快速通道时间表，以考虑一项新法律的法律挑战，该法律要求中国字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前剥离 TikTok 在美国的资产，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-hear-challenges-potential-tiktok-ban-september-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪推出新混合动力技术，与汽油竞争对手的竞争愈演愈烈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-launches-new-hybrid-vehicle-tech-with-lower-fuel-consumption-2024-05-28/</link><description>中国比亚迪周二推出了最新版本的插电式混合动力技术，该技术可改善燃油并节省成本，加剧了与仍主要销售汽油车的丰田和大众等公司的竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:30:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-launches-new-hybrid-vehicle-tech-with-lower-fuel-consumption-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人寻求投资者重组</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-liquidators-seek-investors-restructuring-2024-05-28/</link><description>房地产公司中国恒大集团周二表示，其清算人仅对公司资产进行了“适度变现”，目前正在寻找投资者进行重组。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:23:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-liquidators-seek-investors-restructuring-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>郑在法国公开赛上大获全胜，让科内特退役</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-sends-cornet-into-retirement-with-french-open-thumping-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，七号种子郑沁文以6-2 6-1击败阿莉兹·科内特，进入法国网球公开赛第二轮，这位法国女单在连续20年在大满贯赛场上惨败，惨遭退役。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:07:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-sends-cornet-into-retirement-with-french-open-thumping-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>当美国迈向更快的股票结算时，其他国家在哪里？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-moves-towards-faster-stock-settlement-where-are-other-countries-2024-05-28/</link><description>美国证券交易委员会于 2023 年 2 月通过一项规则，从周二开始，将证券交易的结算周期从交易后的两个工作日缩短至一个工作日。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-moves-towards-faster-stock-settlement-where-are-other-countries-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>随着替代供应商的出现，美国对中国医疗进口产品的关税面临业界质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-tariffs-chinese-medical-imports-face-industry-doubt-alternative-suppliers-2024-05-28/</link><description>行业高管表示，美国对中国医用手套、注射器和口罩征收更高的关税不太可能使美国生产商更具竞争力，因为其他低成本供应商预计将涌入填补缺口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-tariffs-chinese-medical-imports-face-industry-doubt-alternative-suppliers-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾立法院通过有争议的改革方案，数千人抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-protest-taiwans-parliament-passes-contested-reforms-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，台湾议会通过了一项旨在加强对政府监督的改革方案，该方案由反对派推动，但遭到执政党的反对，而执政党没有足够的人数来阻止该方案，数千人在议会外举行抗议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-protest-taiwans-parliament-passes-contested-reforms-2024-05-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>